sql_query.sql: SELECT categories.id FROM "categories" INNER JOIN "category_groups" ON "categories"."id" = "category_groups"."category_id" INNER JOIN "groups" ON "category_groups"."group_id" = "groups"."id" INNER JOIN "group_users" ON "groups"."id" = "group_users"."group_id" WHERE "group_users"."user_id" = 1327

SELECT "topics"."id" FROM "topics" JOIN topic_search_data s ON topics.id = s.topic_id LEFT JOIN categories c ON topics.id = c.topic_id WHERE ("topics"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "topics"."visible" = TRUE AND (topics.archetype <> 'private_message') AND (topics.category_id IS NULL OR topics.category_id IN (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE NOT read_restricted OR id IN (213))) AND (search_data @@ TO_TSQUERY('english', '''body'':* | ''enough'':* | ''for'':* | ''is'':* | ''long'':* | ''search'':* | ''this'':* | ''title'':* | ''to'':*')) AND (c.topic_id IS NULL) ORDER BY ts_rank(search_data, TO_TSQUERY('english', '''body'':* | ''enough'':* | ''for'':* | ''is'':* | ''long'':* | ''search'':* | ''this'':* | ''title'':* | ''to'':*')) DESC LIMIT 15

sql_query.sql: SELECT topics.*, similarity(topics.title, 'this title is long enough to search for') + similarity(p.raw, 'this body is long enough to search for') AS similarity, p.cooked AS blurb FROM "topics" JOIN posts AS p ON p.topic_id = topics.id AND p.post_number = 1 WHERE ("topics"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND (topics.id IN (1026,1027)) AND (similarity(topics.title, 'this title is long enough to search for') + similarity(p.raw, 'this body is long enough to search for') > 0.2) ORDER BY similarity DESC LIMIT 5
